                "text": "The Mini Sprinkler Sanyantr scheme Under the Agriculture Department Rajasthan government will provide 70% to 75% subsidy to farmers for installing sprinkler plants. Through this farmers can irrigate more land by getting sprinkler subsidy. The subsidy given by the state government to the farmers will be sent directly to their bank accounts through DBT. The income of farmers will improve through this scheme. Apart from this, efficient utilization and production will also increase."
